{"type":"step_start","timestamp":1775818500416,"sessionID":"ses_288fc3978ffestAwKqA90pStH5","part":{"id":"prt_d7707e93d0012MON94EuOoqQUB","messageID":"msg_d7707e08b001PTO1IJAswqL0B7","sessionID":"ses_288fc3978ffestAwKqA90pStH5","snapshot":"f33c5114db06c230ebdbad281b75532a26b6f114","type":"step-start"}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775818502514,"sessionID":"ses_288fc3978ffestAwKqA90pStH5","part":{"id":"prt_d7707ec6b001OK8b66lpKADMFR","messageID":"msg_d7707e08b001PTO1IJAswqL0B7","sessionID":"ses_288fc3978ffestAwKqA90pStH5","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"call_88082f97f5284c5b90934a6a","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-006/delta-spec.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-006/delta-spec.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # AR-006: Sandbox 删除与生命周期管理 — Delta Spec\n2: \n3: ## Purpose\n4: \n5: 为 `pkg/workloadmanager` 模块实现 Sandbox 删除处理器和后台垃圾回收（GC）循环，补全沙箱生命周期的\"删除\"环节。覆盖 `DELETE /v1/agent-runtime/sessions/:sessionId` 和 `DELETE /v1/code-interpreter/sessions/:sessionId` 端点的 handler 实现、Store 条目清理、CR 删除幂等性、认证场景下的 per-user client 使用、每 15 秒 tick 的 GC 循环、以及优雅关闭时后台 worker 的正确退出。本变更是 AR-005（Sandbox 创建处理器）的下游实现，与 AR-004（HTTP 服务框架）和 sandbox-orchestration spec 对齐。\n6: \n7: ## Requirements\n8: \n9: ### Requirement: SandboxDeleteHandler 结构体与依赖注入\n10: \n11: The system SHALL 定义 `SandboxDeleteHandler` 结构体，封装以下依赖：dynamic client（用于删除 Sandbox/SandboxClaim CR）、Store 接口（用于按 session ID 查询和删除会话条目）、TokenCache（用于认证场景下的用户 client 缓存）、UserClientFactory（可选，EnableAuth 时构建 per-user client）、以及 EnableAuth 标志。Handler SHALL 提供构造函数 `NewSandboxDeleteHandler(deps)` 接收依赖结构体。\n12: \n13: #### Scenario: Handler 构造\n14: \n15: - **GIVEN** 所有必需依赖（dynamic client、Store）均已初始化\n16: - **WHEN** `NewSandboxDeleteHandler(deps)` 被调用\n17: - **THEN** 返回非空的 `*SandboxDeleteHandler` 且所有依赖字段已正确赋值\n18: \n19: #### Scenario: 可选依赖为 nil 时不 panic\n20: \n21: - **GIVEN** TokenCache 和 UserClientFactory 为 nil（EnableAuth=false 场景）\n22: - **WHEN** Handler 构造完成\n23: - **THEN** 不 panic，相关字段为 nil，后续代码路径在 EnableAuth=false 时不访问这些字段\n24: \n25: ---\n26: \n27: ### Requirement: DELETE /v1/agent-runtime/sessions/:sessionId — AgentRuntime Sandbox 删除流程\n28: \n29: The system SHALL 实现 `DELETE /v1/agent-runtime/sessions/:sessionId` 端点的 handler，执行以下流程：\n30: 1. 从 Gin 路径参数 `sessionId`（camelCase）提取 session ID\n31: 2. 调用 `Store.GetSandboxBySessionID(ctx, sessionId)` 加载会话信息\n32: 3. 若返回 `ErrNotFound`，返回 HTTP 404，响应体 `{\"message\":\"Session ID <id> not found, maybe already deleted\"}`\n33: 4. 根据 `sandboxInfo.Kind` 选择 GVR：`SandboxClaimsKind` → `SandboxClaimGVR`，否则 → `SandboxGVR`\n34: 5. 通过 dynamic client 删除 CR：`dynClient.Resource(gvr).Namespace(sandboxInfo.Namespace).Delete(ctx, sandboxInfo.SandboxName, metav1.DeleteOptions{})`\n35: 6. 若 API 返回 `apierrors.IsNotFound(err)`，视为删除成功（幂等性）\n36: 7. 调用 `Store.DeleteSandboxBySessionID(ctx, sessionId)` 清理 Store 条目\n37: 8. 成功响应：HTTP 200，响应体 `{\"message\":\"Sandbox deleted successfully\"}`\n38: \n39: #### Scenario: AgentRuntime Sandbox 删除成功\n40: \n41: - **GIVEN** Store 中存在 session ID 为 `test-session-1` 的 SandboxInfo，`Kind` 为 `AgentRuntime`，`SandboxName` 为 `my-runtime-abc12345`，`Namespace` 为 `default`\n42: - **WHEN** 客户端发送 `DELETE /v1/agent-runtime/sessions/test-session-1`\n43: - **THEN** dynamic client 以 `SandboxGVR` 删除 `default/my-runtime-abc12345`\n44: - **AND** `DeleteSandboxBySessionID` 被调用\n45: - **AND** 返回 HTTP 200，响应体 `{\"message\":\"Sandbox deleted successfully\"}`\n46: \n47: #### Scenario: Store 中不存在 session ID\n48: \n49: - **GIVEN** Store 中不存在 session ID 为 `nonexistent-session` 的条目\n50: - **WHEN** 客户端发送 `DELETE /v1/agent-runtime/sessions/nonexistent-session`\n51: - **THEN** 返回 HTTP 404\n52: - **AND** 响应体 `message` 包含 `nonexistent-session`\n53: \n54: #### Scenario: CR 已被删除（幂等性）\n55: \n56: - **GIVEN** Store 中存在 session 条目，但对应的 Sandbox CR 已被其他组件（如 GC 或 agentd）删除\n57: - **WHEN** 客户端发送 `DELETE /v1/agent-runtime/sessions/:sessionId`\n58: - **THEN** dynamic client Delete 返回 `NotFound` 错误\n59: - **AND** Handler 视为删除成功\n60: - **AND** `DeleteSandboxBySessionID` 仍被调用\n61: - **AND** 返回 HTTP 200，响应体 `{\"message\":\"Sandbox deleted successfully\"}`\n62: \n63: #### Scenario: Store 删除失败\n64: \n65: - **GIVEN** CR 删除成功，但 `DeleteSandboxBySessionID` 返回错误（如 Redis 连接断开）\n66: - **WHEN** Handler 执行到 Store 清理步骤\n67: - **THEN** 返回 HTTP 500\n68: - **AND** 响应体 `message` 为 `internal server error` 或具体错误信息\n69: \n70: ---\n71: \n72: ### Requirement: DELETE /v1/code-interpreter/sessions/:sessionId — CodeInterpreter Sandbox 删除流程\n73: \n74: The system SHALL 实现 `DELETE /v1/code-interpreter/sessions/:sessionId` 端点的 handler，流程与 AgentRuntime 删除类似，但有以下差异：\n75: - 当 `sandboxInfo.Kind` 为 `SandboxClaimsKind` 时，使用 `SandboxClaimGVR` 删除 SandboxClaim CR\n76: - 当 `sandboxInfo.Kind` 为 `SandboxesKind` 时，使用 `SandboxGVR` 删除 Sandbox CR\n77: \n78: #### Scenario: CodeInterpreter SandboxClaim 删除成功\n79: \n80: - **GIVEN** Store 中存在 session ID 为 `ci-session-1` 的 SandboxInfo，`Kind` 为 `SandboxClaimsKind`，`SandboxName` 为 `my-ci-claim-xyz78901`，`Namespace` 为 `default`\n81: - **WHEN** 客户端发送 `DELETE /v1/code-interpreter/sessions/ci-session-1`\n82: - **THEN** dynamic client 以 `SandboxClaimGVR` 删除 `default/my-ci-claim-xyz78901`\n83: - **AND** `DeleteSandboxBySessionID` 被调用\n84: - **AND** 返回 HTTP 200，响应体 `{\"message\":\"Sandbox deleted successfully\"}`\n85: \n86: #### Scenario: CodeInterpreter 完整 Sandbox 删除\n87: \n88: - **GIVEN** Store 中存在 session ID 为 `ci-session-2` 的 SandboxInfo，`Kind` 为 `SandboxesKind`（WarmPoolSize=0 场景创建的完整 Sandbox）\n89: - **WHEN** 客户端发送 `DELETE /v1/code-interpreter/sessions/ci-session-2`\n90: - **THEN** dynamic client 以 `SandboxGVR` 删除对应的 Sandbox CR\n91: - **AND** 返回 HTTP 200\n92: \n93: ---\n94: \n95: ### Requirement: GVR 选择逻辑\n96: \n97: The system SHALL 根据 `SandboxInfo.Kind` 字段选择正确的 GVR 用于删除操作：\n98: - `Kind == SandboxClaimsKind`（`\"SandboxClaim\"`）→ `SandboxClaimGVR`（group `extensions.agents.x-k8s.io`, version `v1alpha1`, resource `sandboxclaims`）\n99: - 其他值（包括 `SandboxesKind`/`\"Sandbox\"` 和 `AgentRuntimeKind`/`\"AgentRuntime\"`）→ `SandboxGVR`（group `agents.x-k8s.io`, version `v1alpha1`, resource `sandboxes`）\n100: \n101: #### Scenario: SandboxClaim Kind 映射到 SandboxClaimGVR\n102: \n103: - **GIVEN** `sandboxInfo.Kind` 为 `\"SandboxClaim\"`\n104: - **WHEN** GVR 选择逻辑执行\n105: - **THEN** 使用 `SandboxClaimGVR`（group `extensions.agents.x-k8s.io`, resource `sandboxclaims`）\n106: \n107: #### Scenario: Sandbox Kind 映射到 SandboxGVR\n108: \n109: - **GIVEN** `sandboxInfo.Kind` 为 `\"Sandbox\"`\n110: - **WHEN** GVR 选择逻辑执行\n111: - **THEN** 使用 `SandboxGVR`（group `agents.x-k8s.io`, resource `sandboxes`）\n112: \n113: #### Scenario: AgentRuntime Kind 映射到 SandboxGVR\n114: \n115: - **GIVEN** `sandboxInfo.Kind` 为 `\"AgentRuntime\"`\n116: - **WHEN** GVR 选择逻辑执行\n117: - **THEN** 使用 `SandboxGVR`（group `agents.x-k8s.io`, resource `sandboxes`）\n118: \n119: ---\n120: \n121: ### Requirement: 认证场景下的用户 Client 使用\n122: \n123: When `EnableAuth` is true, the system SHALL 使用基于用户 bearer token 构建的 per-user dynamic client 来删除 Sandbox 或 SandboxClaim 资源。用户 client 的获取方式 SHALL 与创建流程一致：通过 TokenCache 的 `GetOrCreateUserK8sClient(namespace, saName, token)` 或 UserClientFactory 的 `CreateUserClient(token)`。When `EnableAuth` is false, the system SHALL 使用 manager 的 in-cluster dynamic client。\n124: \n125: #### Scenario: EnableAuth=true 使用用户 client 删除\n126: \n127: - **GIVEN** `EnableAuth` 为 true，请求携带有效的 service account bearer token\n128: - **WHEN** 删除流程执行 Delete 操作\n129: - **THEN** 使用从 token 构建的 per-user dynamic client\n130: \n131: #### Scenario: EnableAuth=false 使用 manager client 删除\n132: \n133: - **GIVEN** `EnableAuth` 为 false\n134: - **WHEN** 删除流程执行 Delete 操作\n135: - **THEN** 使用 manager 的 in-cluster dynamic client\n136: \n137: #### Scenario: 认证缺失时返回 401\n138: \n139: - **GIVEN** `EnableAuth` 为 true，请求未携带 `Authorization` header\n140: - **WHEN** Handler 尝试获取 dynamic client\n141: - **THEN** 返回 HTTP 401，响应体 `message` 指明 authorization token is required\n142: \n143: ---\n144: \n145: ### Requirement: 错误响应映射\n146: \n147: The system SHALL 将各类错误映射为统一的 HTTP 错误响应：\n148: - `404` — Store 中不存在 session ID（`ErrNotFound`），响应体 `message` 包含 session id\n149: - `401` — EnableAuth 时 token 缺失或验证失败\n150: - `500` — 内部错误（Store 不可达、dynamic client 删除失败且非 NotFound、Store 清理失败），响应体 `{\"message\": \"internal server error\"}` 或具体错误信息\n151: \n152: #### Scenario: Store 不可达\n153: \n154: - **GIVEN** Store 后端（如 Redis/Valkey）连接断开\n155: - **WHEN** `GetSandboxBySessionID` 被调用\n156: - **THEN** 返回 HTTP 500，响应体 `message` 为 `internal server error`\n157: \n158: #### Scenario: Dynamic client 删除失败（非 NotFound）\n159: \n160: - **GIVEN** dynamic client Delete 返回非 NotFound 错误（如网络超时、权限不足）\n161: - **WHEN** 删除操作执行\n162: - **THEN** 返回 HTTP 500，响应体 `message` 为 `internal server error`\n163: \n164: ---\n165: \n166: ### Requirement: 统一 JSON 响应格式\n167: \n168: The system SHALL 使用 `pkg/workloadmanager/response` 包中的 `JSON()` 和 `Error()` 函数返回响应。成功删除返回 HTTP 200，响应体为 `{\"message\":\"Sandbox deleted successfully\"}`。错误返回使用统一的 `{\"message\": \"...\", \"code\": <int>}` 格式。\n169: \n170: #### Scenario: 成功响应格式\n171: \n172: - **GIVEN** Sandbox 删除成功\n173: - **WHEN** 响应被发送\n174: - **THEN** HTTP 状态码为 200\n175: - **AND** 响应体为 `{\"message\":\"Sandbox deleted successfully\"}`\n176: - **AND** Content-Type 为 `application/json`\n177: \n178: #### Scenario: 错误响应格式\n179: \n180: - **GIVEN** 删除流程中发生错误\n181: - **WHEN** 错误响应被发送\n182: - **THEN** 响应体为 `{\"message\": \"<error message>\", \"code\": <error code>}`\n183: - **AND** Content-Type 为 `application/json`\n184: \n185: ---\n186: \n187: ### Requirement: Garbage Collector 循环\n188: \n189: The system SHALL 实现后台 `garbageCollector` 结构体，运行一个后台 goroutine，tick 间隔为 15 秒。每次 tick SHALL：\n190: 1. 创建超时为 2 分钟的 context\n191: 2. 调用 `ListInactiveSandboxes(ctx, time.Now().Add(-DefaultSandboxIdleTimeout), 16)` 获取空闲沙箱（`DefaultSandboxIdleTimeout` = 15 分钟）\n192: 3. 调用 `ListExpiredSandboxes(ctx, time.Now(), 16)` 获取过期沙箱（`ExpiresAt < now`）\n193: 4. 合并两列表，按 session ID 去重\n194: 5. 对每个唯一 session：\n195:    a. 加载 `SandboxInfo`\n196:    b. 根据 `Kind` 选择 GVR 并删除 CR（NotFound 视为成功）\n197:    c. 调用 `DeleteSandboxBySessionID` 清理 Store\n198: 6. 记录删除统计日志（成功/失败数量）\n199: \n200: #### Scenario: GC tick 间隔为 15 秒\n201: \n202: - **GIVEN** GC goroutine 已启动\n203: - **WHEN** 时间流逝\n204: - **THEN** GC 每 15 秒执行一次 tick\n205: \n206: #### Scenario: GC 使用 2 分钟超时 context\n207: \n208: - **GIVEN** GC 开始一次 tick\n209: - **WHEN** tick 执行 ListInactiveSandboxes 和 ListExpiredSandboxes\n210: - **THEN** 使用的 context 超时为 2 分钟\n211: \n212: #### Scenario: GC 查询空闲沙箱使用 15 分钟 cutoff\n213: \n214: - **GIVEN** GC 计算 inactive cutoff\n215: - **WHEN** `ListInactiveSandboxes` 被调用\n216: - **THEN** `before` 参数为 `time.Now().Add(-15 * time.Minute)`\n217: - **AND** `limit` 参数为 16\n218: \n219: #### Scenario: GC 查询过期沙箱使用 now 作为 cutoff\n220: \n221: - **GIVEN** GC 计算 expired cutoff\n222: - **WHEN** `ListExpiredSandboxes` 被调用\n223: - **THEN** `before` 参数为 `time.Now()`\n224: - **AND** `limit` 参数为 16\n225: \n226: #### Scenario: GC 去重处理同一 session 同时出现在两个列表\n227: \n228: - **GIVEN** 某个 session 同时出现在空闲列表和过期列表中\n229: - **WHEN** GC 合并两列表\n230: - **THEN** 该 session 只被处理一次（按 session ID 去重）\n231: \n232: #### Scenario: GC 删除 CR 时 NotFound 视为成功\n233: \n234: - **GIVEN** GC 尝试删除某 Sandbox CR，但 CR 已被 agentd idle-cleanup controller 删除\n235: - **WHEN** dynamic client Delete 返回 `NotFound` 错误\n236: - **THEN** GC 视为删除成功\n237: - **AND** 继续调用 `DeleteSandboxBySessionID` 清理 Store\n238: \n239: #### Scenario: GC 记录删除统计日志\n240: \n241: - **GIVEN** GC 完成一次 tick，处理了 5 个 session（3 成功，2 失败）\n242: - **WHEN** tick 结束\n243: - **THEN** 日志记录成功和失败的删除数量\n244: \n245: #### Scenario: GC 在 Store 为空时不执行删除\n246: \n247: - **GIVEN** Store 中没有任何过期或空闲沙箱\n248: - **WHEN** GC 执行 tick\n249: - **THEN** `ListInactiveSandboxes` 和 `ListExpiredSandboxes` 返回空列表\n250: - **AND** 不执行任何删除操作\n251: \n252: ---\n253: \n254: ### Requirement: Garbage Collector 启动与停止\n255: \n256: The system SHALL 提供 `garbageCollector.Start(ctx)` 方法，启动后台 goroutine 并在 context 取消时退出。The system SHALL 提供 `garbageCollector.Stop()` 或依赖 context 取消来停止 GC 循环。GC goroutine 退出后 SHALL 通知调用方（通过 channel 或 WaitGroup）。\n257: \n258: #### Scenario: GC 启动后开始 tick\n259: \n260: - **GIVEN** `garbageCollector.Start(ctx)` 被调用，ctx 未取消\n261: - **WHEN** GC goroutine 启动\n262: - **THEN** 开始按 15 秒间隔执行 tick\n263: \n264: #### Scenario: GC 在 context 取消后退出\n265: \n266: - **GIVEN** GC goroutine 正在运行\n267: - **WHEN** `ctx.Done()` 被触发\n268: - **THEN** GC goroutine 退出循环\n269: - **AND** 不再执行新的 tick\n270: \n271: #### Scenario: GC 在 tick 进行中 context 取消\n272: \n273: - **GIVEN** GC 正在执行一次 tick（2 分钟超时 context 内）\n274: - **WHEN** 主 context 被取消\n275: - **THEN** GC 在当前 tick 完成后退出（或 tick context 被取消导致提前退出）\n276: \n277: ---\n278: \n279: ### Requirement: 优雅关闭\n280: \n281: The system SHALL 在进程收到 SIGINT/SIGTERM 时按以下顺序执行优雅关闭：\n282: 1. HTTP server shutdown（超时 15 秒）\n283: 2. 取消 GC context，等待 GC goroutine 退出\n284: 3. 调用 `store.Close()` 关闭 Store 连接\n285: \n286: #### Scenario: 优雅关闭顺序正确\n287: \n288: - **GIVEN** 进程收到 SIGTERM 信号\n289: - **WHEN** 优雅关闭流程执行\n290: - **THEN** HTTP server 先 shutdown（15s 超时）\n291: - **AND** GC goroutine 被通知退出并等待其完成\n292: - **AND** Store.Close() 最后调用\n293: \n294: #### Scenario: 无 goroutine 泄漏\n295: \n296: - **GIVEN** 优雅关闭完成\n297: - **WHEN** 进程退出\n298: - **THEN** 所有后台 goroutine（GC、watcher 等）已正确退出\n299: - **AND** 无 goroutine 泄漏\n300: \n301: ---\n302: \n303: ### Requirement: 删除流程的端到端排序\n304: \n305: The system SHALL 严格按以下顺序执行 Sandbox 删除流程：\n306: 1. 从路径提取 `sessionId` → 2. `Store.GetSandboxBySessionID` 加载会话 → 3. 选择 GVR → 4. 获取 dynamic client（认证场景使用 per-user client）→ 5. Dynamic Client Delete CR（NotFound 视为成功）→ 6. `Store.DeleteSandboxBySessionID` 清理 Store → 7. 返回 200 成功响应\n307: \n308: 任何步骤失败 SHALL 返回适当的错误响应（404/401/500），不继续后续步骤。\n309: \n310: #### Scenario: 完整成功路径\n311: \n312: - **GIVEN** Store 中存在有效 session 条目，对应 CR 存在，Store 和 API server 可用\n313: - **WHEN** `DELETE /v1/agent-runtime/sessions/:sessionId` 被调用\n314: - **THEN** 以上 7 个步骤依次执行，最终返回 200\n315: \n316: #### Scenario: 步骤 2 失败（Store 中不存在）不执行后续步骤\n317: \n318: - **GIVEN** Store 中不存在该 session ID\n319: - **WHEN** 删除流程执行到步骤 2\n320: - **THEN** 返回 404，不执行步骤 3-7\n321: \n322: #### Scenario: 步骤 5 失败（非 NotFound 错误）不执行 Store 清理\n323: \n324: - **GIVEN** dynamic client Delete 返回非 NotFound 错误（如权限不足）\n325: - **WHEN** 删除流程执行到步骤 5\n326: - **THEN** 返回 500，不执行步骤 6（Store 清理）\n\n(End of file - total 326 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AR-006: Sandbox 删除与生命周期管理 — Delta Spec\n\n## Purpose\n\n为 `pkg/workloadmanager` 模块实现 Sandbox 删除处理器和后台垃圾回收（GC）循环，补全沙箱生命周期的\"删除\"环节。覆盖 `DELETE /v1/agent-runtime/sessions/:sessionId` 和 `DELETE /v1/code-interpreter/sessions/:sessionId` 端点的 handler 实现、Store 条目清理、CR 删除幂等性、认证场景下的 per-user client 使用、每 15 秒 tick 的 GC 循环、以及优雅关闭时后台 worker 的正确退出。本变更是 AR-005（Sandbox 创建处理器）的下游实现，与 AR-004（HTTP 服务框架）和 sandbox-orchestration spec 对齐。\n\n## Requirements\n\n### Requirement: SandboxDeleteHandler 结构体与依赖注入\n\nThe system SHALL 定义 `SandboxDeleteHandler` 结构体，封装以下依赖：dynamic client（用于删除 Sandbox/SandboxClaim CR）、Store 接口（用于按 session ID 查询和删除会话条目）、TokenCache（用于认证场景下的用户 client 缓存）、UserClientFactory（可选，EnableAuth 时构建 per-user client）、以及 EnableAuth 标志。Handler SHALL 提供构造函数 `NewSandboxDeleteHandler(deps)` 接收依赖结构体。\n\n#### Scenario: Handler 构造\n\n- **GIVEN** 所有必需依赖（dynamic client、Store）均已初始化\n- **WHEN** `NewSandboxDeleteHandler(deps)` 被调用\n- **THEN** 返回非空的 `*SandboxDeleteHandler` 且所有依赖字段已正确赋值\n\n#### Scenario: 可选依赖为 nil 时不 panic\n","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-006/delta-spec.md","time":{"start":1775818502505,"end":1775818502512}}}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775818504414,"sessionID":"ses_288fc3978ffestAwKqA90pStH5","part":{"id":"prt_d7707f375001n68XdJehClTx1b","messageID":"msg_d7707e08b001PTO1IJAswqL0B7","sessionID":"ses_288fc3978ffestAwKqA90pStH5","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"call_982c526eb4a04b3ea5ebad88","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-006/design.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-006/design.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # AR-006: Sandbox 删除与生命周期管理\n2: \n3: ## Overview\n4: \n5: <!-- Describe the sandbox deletion and lifecycle management feature -->\n6: \n7: ## Context\n8: \n9: <!-- Why is this change needed? What problem does it solve? -->\n10: \n11: ## Goals\n12: \n13: <!-- What are the success criteria? -->\n14: \n15: ## Non-Goals\n16: \n17: <!-- What is explicitly out of scope? -->\n18: \n19: ## Design\n20: \n21: <!-- Technical design details -->\n22: \n23: ## Alternatives Considered\n24: \n25: <!-- What other approaches were considered and why were they rejected? -->\n\n(End of file - total 25 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AR-006: Sandbox 删除与生命周期管理\n\n## Overview\n\n<!-- Describe the sandbox deletion and lifecycle management feature -->\n\n## Context\n\n<!-- Why is this change needed? What problem does it solve? -->\n\n## Goals\n\n<!-- What are the success criteria? -->\n\n## Non-Goals\n\n<!-- What is explicitly out of scope? -->\n\n## Design\n","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-006/design.md","time":{"start":1775818504400,"end":1775818504413}}}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775818505912,"sessionID":"ses_288fc3978ffestAwKqA90pStH5","part":{"id":"prt_d7707f9df0017DfX4VMCjbA6C5","messageID":"msg_d7707e08b001PTO1IJAswqL0B7","sessionID":"ses_288fc3978ffestAwKqA90pStH5","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"call_d0b1ac4993084a0d83fed418","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/pkg/workloadmanager/handler/sandbox_create.go"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/pkg/workloadmanager/handler/sandbox_create.go</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: package handler\n2: \n3: import (\n4: \t\"context\"\n5: \t\"fmt\"\n6: \t\"log\"\n7: \t\"math/rand\"\n8: \t\"net/http\"\n9: \t\"time\"\n10: \n11: \t\"github.com/gin-gonic/gin\"\n12: \t\"github.com/google/uuid\"\n13: \tcorev1 \"k8s.io/api/core/v1\"\n14: \tapierrors \"k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/api/errors\"\n15: \tmetav1 \"k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/apis/meta/v1\"\n16: \t\"k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/apis/meta/v1/unstructured\"\n17: \t\"k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/labels\"\n18: \t\"k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/runtime\"\n19: \t\"k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/runtime/schema\"\n20: \t\"k8s.io/client-go/dynamic\"\n21: \t\"k8s.io/client-go/informers\"\n22: \t\"k8s.io/client-go/kubernetes\"\n23: \n24: \t\"github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/client-go/clientset\"\n25: \truntimev1alpha1 \"github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1\"\n26: \t\"github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/pkg/workloadmanager/response\"\n27: )\n28: \n29: type Store interface {\n30: \tStoreSandbox(ctx context.Context, info *SandboxInfo) error\n31: \tUpdateSandbox(ctx context.Context, sessionID string, info *SandboxInfo) error\n32: }\n33: \n34: type SandboxReconcilerWatcher interface {\n35: \tWatchSandboxOnce(namespace, name string) (<-chan SandboxStatus, error)\n36: }\n37: \n38: type TokenCache interface {\n39: \tGetOrCreateUserK8sClient(namespace, saName, token string) (dynamic.Interface, error)\n40: }\n41: \n42: type SandboxCreateHandlerDeps struct {\n43: \tDynamicClient     dynamic.Interface\n44: \tClientset         clientset.Interface\n45: \tInformerFactory   informers.SharedInformerFactory\n46: \tStore             Store\n47: \tReconciler        SandboxReconcilerWatcher\n48: \tTokenCache        TokenCache\n49: \tUserClientFactory UserClientFactory\n50: \tEnableAuth        bool\n51: }\n52: \n53: type UserClientFactory interface {\n54: \tCreateUserClient(token string) (dynamic.Interface, error)\n55: }\n56: \n57: type SandboxCreateHandler struct {\n58: \tdynamicClient     dynamic.Interface\n59: \tclientset         clientset.Interface\n60: \tinformerFactory   informers.SharedInformerFactory\n61: \tstore             Store\n62: \treconciler        SandboxReconcilerWatcher\n63: \ttokenCache        TokenCache\n64: \tuserClientFactory UserClientFactory\n65: \tenableAuth        bool\n66: }\n67: \n68: func NewSandboxCreateHandler(deps *SandboxCreateHandlerDeps) *SandboxCreateHandler {\n69: \treturn &SandboxCreateHandler{\n70: \t\tdynamicClient:     deps.DynamicClient,\n71: \t\tclientset:         deps.Clientset,\n72: \t\tinformerFactory:   deps.InformerFactory,\n73: \t\tstore:             deps.Store,\n74: \t\treconciler:        deps.Reconciler,\n75: \t\ttokenCache:        deps.TokenCache,\n76: \t\tuserClientFactory: deps.UserClientFactory,\n77: \t\tenableAuth:        deps.EnableAuth,\n78: \t}\n79: }\n80: \n81: func (h *SandboxCreateHandler) getDynamicClient(c *gin.Context) (dynamic.Interface, error) {\n82: \tif !h.enableAuth {\n83: \t\treturn h.dynamicClient, nil\n84: \t}\n85: \n86: \ttoken := c.GetHeader(\"Authorization\")\n87: \tif token == \"\" {\n88: \t\treturn nil, fmt.Errorf(\"authorization token is required\")\n89: \t}\n90: \tif len(token) > 7 && token[:7] == \"Bearer \" {\n91: \t\ttoken = token[7:]\n92: \t}\n93: \n94: \tnamespace := c.GetString(\"namespace\")\n95: \tsaName := c.GetString(\"serviceAccountName\")\n96: \n97: \tif h.tokenCache != nil {\n98: \t\treturn h.tokenCache.GetOrCreateUserK8sClient(namespace, saName, token)\n99: \t}\n100: \n101: \tif h.userClientFactory != nil {\n102: \t\treturn h.userClientFactory.CreateUserClient(token)\n103: \t}\n104: \n105: \treturn nil, fmt.Errorf(\"no user client factory available\")\n106: }\n107: \n108: func (h *SandboxCreateHandler) CreateAgentRuntimeSandbox(c *gin.Context) {\n109: \tvar sandboxReq CreateSandboxRequest\n110: \tif err := c.ShouldBindJSON(&sandboxReq); err != nil {\n111: \t\tresponse.Error(c, http.StatusBadRequest, http.StatusBadRequest, \"Invalid request body\")\n112: \t\treturn\n113: \t}\n114: \n115: \tsandboxReq.Kind = AgentRuntimeKind\n116: \n117: \tif err := sandboxReq.Validate(); err != nil {\n118: \t\tresponse.Error(c, http.StatusBadRequest, http.StatusBadRequest, err.Error())\n119: \t\treturn\n120: \t}\n121: \n122: \tarLister := h.informerFactory.Runtime().V1alpha1().AgentRuntimes().Lister()\n123: \ttemplate, err := arLister.AgentRuntimes(sandboxReq.Namespace).Get(sandboxReq.Name)\n124: \tif err != nil {\n125: \t\tresponse.Error(c, http.StatusNotFound, http.StatusNotFound, fmt.Sprintf(\"AgentRuntime %s/%s not found\", sandboxReq.Namespace, sandboxReq.Name))\n126: \t\treturn\n127: \t}\n128: \n129: \tif template.Spec.Template == nil {\n130: \t\tresponse.Error(c, http.StatusBadRequest, http.StatusBadRequest, \"podTemplate is required\")\n131: \t\treturn\n132: \t}\n133: \n134: \tsessionID := generateSessionID()\n135: \tsandboxName := generateSandboxName(sandboxReq.Name)\n136: \n137: \tsandboxCR, err := h.buildAgentRuntimeSandboxCR(template, sessionID, sandboxName, sandboxReq.Name, sandboxReq.Namespace)\n138: \tif err != nil {\n139: \t\tresponse.Error(c, http.StatusInternalServerError, http.StatusInternalServerError, \"internal server error\")\n140: \t\treturn\n141: \t}\n142: \n143: \tsandboxInfo := &SandboxInfo{\n144: \t\tSessionID:    sessionID,\n145: \t\tSandboxName:  sandboxName,\n146: \t\tWorkloadName: sandboxReq.Name,\n147: \t\tNamespace:    sandboxReq.Namespace,\n148: \t\tKind:         AgentRuntimeKind,\n149: \t\tStatus:       \"pending\",\n150: \t\tCreatedAt:    time.Now(),\n151: \t}\n152: \n153: \tif err := h.store.StoreSandbox(c.Request.Context(), sandboxInfo); err != nil {\n154: \t\tresponse.Error(c, http.StatusInternalServerError, http.StatusInternalServerError, \"internal server error\")\n155: \t\treturn\n156: \t}\n157: \n158: \twatcherCh, err := h.reconciler.WatchSandboxOnce(sandboxReq.Namespace, sandboxName)\n159: \tif err != nil {\n160: \t\tresponse.Error(c, http.StatusInternalServerError, http.StatusInternalServerError, \"internal server error\")\n161: \t\treturn\n162: \t}\n163: \n164: \tdynClient, err := h.getDynamicClient(c)\n165: \tif err != nil {\n166: \t\tresponse.Error(c, http.StatusUnauthorized, http.StatusUnauthorized, err.Error())\n167: \t\treturn\n168: \t}\n169: \n170: \tcreatedCR, err := dynClient.Resource(SandboxGVR).Namespace(sandboxReq.Namespace).Create(c.Request.Context(), sandboxCR, metav1.CreateOptions{})\n171: \tif err != nil {\n172: \t\tresponse.Error(c, http.StatusInternalServerError, http.StatusInternalServerError, \"internal server error\")\n173: \t\treturn\n174: \t}\n175: \n176: \tctx, cancel := context.WithTimeout(c.Request.Context(), 2*time.Minute)\n177: \tdefer cancel()\n178: \n179: \tselect {\n180: \tcase status := <-watcherCh:\n181: \t\tif status.Error != nil {\n182: \t\t\th.rollbackCR(c.Request.Context(), SandboxGVR, sandboxReq.Namespace, sandboxName, dynClient)\n183: \t\t\tresponse.Error(c, http.StatusInternalServerError, http.StatusInternalServerError, status.Error.Error())\n184: \t\t\treturn\n185: \t\t}\n186: \t\tif status.Status != \"running\" {\n187: \t\t\th.rollbackCR(c.Request.Context(), SandboxGVR, sandboxReq.Namespace, sandboxName, dynClient)\n188: \t\t\tresponse.Error(c, http.StatusInternalServerError, http.StatusInternalServerError, \"sandbox creation timed out\")\n189: \t\t\treturn\n190: \t\t}\n191: \tcase <-ctx.Done():\n192: \t\th.rollbackCR(c.Request.Context(), SandboxGVR, sandboxReq.Namespace, sandboxName, dynClient)\n193: \t\tresponse.Error(c, http.StatusInternalServerError, http.StatusInternalServerError, \"sandbox creation timed out\")\n194: \t\treturn\n195: \t}\n196: \n197: \tpodIP, err := h.resolvePodIP(c.Request.Context(), sandboxName, sandboxReq.Namespace, sandboxCR, h.clientset.CoreV1().(*kubernetes.Clientset))\n198: \tif err != nil {\n199: \t\th.rollbackCR(c.Request.Context(), SandboxGVR, sandboxReq.Namespace, sandboxName, dynClient)\n200: \t\tresponse.Error(c, http.StatusInternalServerError, http.StatusInternalServerError, err.Error())\n201: \t\treturn\n202: \t}\n203: \n204: \tports := template.Spec.Ports\n205: \tentryPoints := h.buildEntryPoints(podIP, ports)\n206: \n207: \tsandboxInfo.SandboxID = string(createdCR.GetUID())\n208: \tsandboxInfo.PodIP = podIP\n209: \tsandboxInfo.EntryPoints = entryPoints\n210: \tsandboxInfo.Status = \"running\"\n211: \n212: \tif err := h.store.UpdateSandbox(c.Request.Context(), sessionID, sandboxInfo); err != nil {\n213: \t\tlog.Printf(\"failed to update sandbox in store: %v\", err)\n214: \t}\n215: \n216: \tresp := &CreateSandboxResponse{\n217: \t\tSessionID:   sessionID,\n218: \t\tSandboxID:   sandboxInfo.SandboxID,\n219: \t\tSandboxName: sandboxName,\n220: \t\tEntryPoints: entryPoints,\n221: \t}\n222: \n223: \tresponse.JSON(c, http.StatusOK, resp)\n224: }\n225: \n226: func (h *SandboxCreateHandler) CreateCodeInterpreterSandbox(c *gin.Context) {\n227: \tvar sandboxReq CreateSandboxRequest\n228: \tif err := c.ShouldBindJSON(&sandboxReq); err != nil {\n229: \t\tresponse.Error(c, http.StatusBadRequest, http.StatusBadRequest, \"Invalid request body\")\n230: \t\treturn\n231: \t}\n232: \n233: \tsandboxReq.Kind = CodeInterpreterKind\n234: \n235: \tif err := sandboxReq.Validate(); err != nil {\n236: \t\tresponse.Error(c, http.StatusBadRequest, http.StatusBadRequest, err.Error())\n237: \t\treturn\n238: \t}\n239: \n240: \tciLister := h.informerFactory.Runtime().V1alpha1().CodeInterpreters().Lister()\n241: \ttemplate, err := ciLister.CodeInterpreters(sandboxReq.Namespace).Get(sandboxReq.Name)\n242: \tif err != nil {\n243: \t\tresponse.Error(c, http.StatusNotFound, http.StatusNotFound, fmt.Sprintf(\"CodeInterpreter %s/%s not found\", sandboxReq.Namespace, sandboxReq.Name))\n244: \t\treturn\n245: \t}\n246: \n247: \tif template.Spec.Template == nil {\n248: \t\tresponse.Error(c, http.StatusBadRequest, http.StatusBadRequest, \"template is required\")\n249: \t\treturn\n250: \t}\n251: \n252: \tsessionID := generateSessionID()\n253: \tsandboxName := generateSandboxName(sandboxReq.Name)\n254: \n255: \tports := getPortsOrDefaults(template.Spec.Ports)\n256: \n257: \tvar sandboxCR *unstructured.Unstructured\n258: \tvar entryKind string\n259: \tvar err error\n260: \n261: \tsandboxCR, entryKind, err = h.buildCodeInterpreterSandboxCR(template, sessionID, sandboxName, sandboxReq.Name, sandboxReq.Namespace, ports)\n262: \tif err != nil {\n263: \t\tresponse.Error(c, http.StatusInternalServerError, http.StatusInternalServerError, \"internal server error\")\n264: \t\treturn\n265: \t}\n266: \n267: \tif template.Spec.AuthMode == runtimev1alpha1.AuthModePicoD {\n268: \t\tif err := h.injectPicodAuthEnv(sandboxCR, sandboxReq.Namespace, h.clientset.CoreV1().(*kubernetes.Clientset)); err != nil {\n269: \t\t\tresponse.Error(c, http.StatusUnauthorized, http.StatusUnauthorized, err.Error())\n270: \t\t\treturn\n271: \t\t}\n272: \t}\n273: \n274: \tsandboxInfo := &SandboxInfo{\n275: \t\tSessionID:    sessionID,\n276: \t\tSandboxName:  sandboxName,\n277: \t\tWorkloadName: sandboxReq.Name,\n278: \t\tNamespace:    sandboxReq.Namespace,\n279: \t\tKind:         entryKind,\n280: \t\tStatus:       \"pending\",\n281: \t\tCreatedAt:    time.Now(),\n282: \t}\n283: \n284: \tif err := h.store.StoreSandbox(c.Request.Context(), sandboxInfo); err != nil {\n285: \t\tresponse.Error(c, http.StatusInternalServerError, http.StatusInternalServerError, \"internal server error\")\n286: \t\treturn\n287: \t}\n288: \n289: \twatcherCh, err := h.reconciler.WatchSandboxOnce(sandboxReq.Namespace, sandboxName)\n290: \tif err != nil {\n291: \t\tresponse.Error(c, http.StatusInternalServerError, http.StatusInternalServerError, \"internal server error\")\n292: \t\treturn\n293: \t}\n294: \n295: \tdynClient, err := h.getDynamicClient(c)\n296: \tif err != nil {\n297: \t\tresponse.Error(c, http.StatusUnauthorized, http.StatusUnauthorized, err.Error())\n298: \t\treturn\n299: \t}\n300: \n301: \tvar gvr schema.GroupVersionResource\n302: \tif entryKind == SandboxClaimsKind {\n303: \t\tgvr = SandboxClaimGVR\n304: \t} else {\n305: \t\tgvr = SandboxGVR\n306: \t}\n307: \n308: \tcreatedCR, err := dynClient.Resource(gvr).Namespace(sandboxReq.Namespace).Create(c.Request.Context(), sandboxCR, metav1.CreateOptions{})\n309: \tif err != nil {\n310: \t\tresponse.Error(c, http.StatusInternalServerError, http.StatusInternalServerError, \"internal server error\")\n311: \t\treturn\n312: \t}\n313: \n314: \tctx, cancel := context.WithTimeout(c.Request.Context(), 2*time.Minute)\n315: \tdefer cancel()\n316: \n317: \tselect {\n318: \tcase status := <-watcherCh:\n319: \t\tif status.Error != nil {\n320: \t\t\th.rollbackCR(c.Request.Context(), gvr, sandboxReq.Namespace, sandboxName, dynClient)\n321: \t\t\tresponse.Error(c, http.StatusInternalServerError, http.StatusInternalServerError, status.Error.Error())\n322: \t\t\treturn\n323: \t\t}\n324: \t\tif status.Status != \"running\" {\n325: \t\t\th.rollbackCR(c.Request.Context(), gvr, sandboxReq.Namespace, sandboxName, dynClient)\n326: \t\t\tresponse.Error(c, http.StatusInternalServerError, http.StatusInternalServerError, \"sandbox creation timed out\")\n327: \t\t\treturn\n328: \t\t}\n329: \tcase <-ctx.Done():\n330: \t\th.rollbackCR(c.Request.Context(), gvr, sandboxReq.Namespace, sandboxName, dynClient)\n331: \t\tresponse.Error(c, http.StatusInternalServerError, http.StatusInternalServerError, \"sandbox creation timed out\")\n332: \t\treturn\n333: \t}\n334: \n335: \tpodIP, err := h.resolvePodIP(c.Request.Context(), sandboxName, sandboxReq.Namespace, sandboxCR, h.clientset.CoreV1().(*kubernetes.Clientset))\n336: \tif err != nil {\n337: \t\th.rollbackCR(c.Request.Context(), gvr, sandboxReq.Namespace, sandboxName, dynClient)\n338: \t\tresponse.Error(c, http.StatusInternalServerError, http.StatusInternalServerError, err.Error())\n339: \t\treturn\n340: \t}\n341: \n342: \tentryPoints := h.buildEntryPoints(podIP, ports)\n343: \n344: \tsandboxInfo.SandboxID = string(createdCR.GetUID())\n345: \tsandboxInfo.PodIP = podIP\n346: \tsandboxInfo.EntryPoints = entryPoints\n347: \tsandboxInfo.Status = \"running\"\n348: \n349: \tif err := h.store.UpdateSandbox(c.Request.Context(), sessionID, sandboxInfo); err != nil {\n350: \t\tlog.Printf(\"failed to update sandbox in store: %v\", err)\n351: \t}\n352: \n353: \tresp := &CreateSandboxResponse{\n354: \t\tSessionID:   sessionID,\n355: \t\tSandboxID:   sandboxInfo.SandboxID,\n356: \t\tSandboxName: sandboxName,\n357: \t\tEntryPoints: entryPoints,\n358: \t}\n359: \n360: \tresponse.JSON(c, http.StatusOK, resp)\n361: }\n362: \n363: func (h *SandboxCreateHandler) rollbackCR(ctx context.Context, gvr schema.GroupVersionResource, namespace, name string, dynClient dynamic.Interface) error {\n364: \trollbackCtx, cancel := context.WithTimeout(ctx, 30*time.Second)\n365: \tdefer cancel()\n366: \n367: \terr := dynClient.Resource(gvr).Namespace(namespace).Delete(rollbackCtx, name, metav1.DeleteOptions{})\n368: \tif err != nil && apierrors.IsNotFound(err) {\n369: \t\treturn nil\n370: \t}\n371: \treturn err\n372: }\n373: \n374: func (h *SandboxCreateHandler) buildAgentRuntimeSandboxCR(template *runtimev1alpha1.AgentRuntime, sessionID, sandboxName, workloadName, namespace string) (*unstructured.Unstructured, error) {\n375: \tcr := &unstructured.Unstructured{}\n376: \tcr.SetAPIVersion(\"agents.x-k8s.io/v1alpha1\")\n377: \tcr.SetKind(\"Sandbox\")\n378: \tcr.SetName(sandboxName)\n379: \tcr.SetNamespace(namespace)\n380: \n381: \tcr.SetLabels(map[string]string{\n382: \t\tLabelManagedBy:    LabelManagedByValue,\n383: \t\tLabelSessionID:    sessionID,\n384: \t\tLabelWorkloadName: workloadName,\n385: \t\tLabelSandboxName:  sandboxName,\n386: \t})\n387: \n388: \tidleTimeout := DefaultSandboxIdleTimeout\n389: \tif template.Spec.SessionTimeout != nil {\n390: \t\tidleTimeout = int(template.Spec.SessionTimeout.Duration.Minutes())\n391: \t}\n392: \tcr.SetAnnotations(map[string]string{\n393: \t\tAnnotationIdleTimeout: fmt.Sprintf(\"%dm\", idleTimeout),\n394: \t})\n395: \n396: \tttl := DefaultSandboxTTL\n397: \tif template.Spec.MaxSessionDuration != nil {\n398: \t\tttl = template.Spec.MaxSessionDuration.Duration.Hours()\n399: \t}\n400: \tshutdownTime := time.Now().Add(time.Duration(ttl) * time.Hour)\n401: \n402: \tspec := map[string]interface{}{\n403: \t\t\"replicas\": int64(1),\n404: \t\t\"lifecycle\": map[string]interface{}{\n405: \t\t\t\"shutdownTime\": shutdownTime.Format(time.RFC3339),\n406: \t\t},\n407: \t}\n408: \n409: \tvar ports []interface{}\n410: \tfor _, p := range template.Spec.Ports {\n411: \t\tports = append(ports, map[string]interface{}{\n412: \t\t\t\"name\":     p.Name,\n413: \t\t\t\"port\":     int64(p.Port),\n414: \t\t\t\"protocol\": string(p.Protocol),\n415: \t\t})\n416: \t}\n417: \tif len(ports) > 0 {\n418: \t\tspec[\"ports\"] = ports\n419: \t}\n420: \n421: \tpodSpec := template.Spec.Template.Spec\n422: \tpodSpecMap, err := runtime.DefaultUnstructuredConverter.ToUnstructured(&podSpec)\n423: \tif err != nil {\n424: \t\treturn nil, fmt.Errorf(\"failed to convert pod spec: %w\", err)\n425: \t}\n426: \tspec[\"podTemplate\"] = podSpecMap\n427: \n428: \tcr.Object[\"spec\"] = spec\n429: \n430: \treturn cr, nil\n431: }\n432: \n433: func (h *SandboxCreateHandler) buildCodeInterpreterSandboxCR(template *runtimev1alpha1.CodeInterpreter, sessionID, sandboxName, workloadName, namespace string, ports []runtimev1alpha1.TargetPort) (*unstructured.Unstructured, string, error) {\n434: \twarmPoolSize := int32(0)\n435: \tif template.Spec.WarmPoolSize != nil {\n436: \t\twarmPoolSize = *template.Spec.WarmPoolSize\n437: \t}\n438: \n439: \tif warmPoolSize > 0 {\n440: \t\tcr := &unstructured.Unstructured{}\n441: \t\tcr.SetAPIVersion(\"extensions.agents.x-k8s.io/v1alpha1\")\n442: \t\tcr.SetKind(\"SandboxClaim\")\n443: \t\tcr.SetName(sandboxName)\n444: \t\tcr.SetNamespace(namespace)\n445: \n446: \t\tcr.SetLabels(map[string]string{\n447: \t\t\tLabelManagedBy:    LabelManagedByValue,\n448: \t\t\tLabelSessionID:    sessionID,\n449: \t\t\tLabelWorkloadName: workloadName,\n450: \t\t\tLabelSandboxName:  sandboxName,\n451: \t\t})\n452: \n453: \t\tidleTimeout := DefaultSandboxIdleTimeout\n454: \t\tif template.Spec.SessionTimeout != nil {\n455: \t\t\tidleTimeout = int(template.Spec.SessionTimeout.Duration.Minutes())\n456: \t\t}\n457: \t\tcr.SetAnnotations(map[string]string{\n458: \t\t\tAnnotationIdleTimeout: fmt.Sprintf(\"%dm\", idleTimeout),\n459: \t\t})\n460: \n461: \t\treturn cr, SandboxClaimsKind, nil\n462: \t}\n463: \n464: \tcr := &unstructured.Unstructured{}\n465: \tcr.SetAPIVersion(\"agents.x-k8s.io/v1alpha1\")\n466: \tcr.SetKind(\"Sandbox\")\n467: \tcr.SetName(sandboxName)\n468: \tcr.SetNamespace(namespace)\n469: \n470: \tcr.SetLabels(map[string]string{\n471: \t\tLabelManagedBy:    LabelManagedByValue,\n472: \t\tLabelSessionID:    sessionID,\n473: \t\tLabelWorkloadName: workloadName,\n474: \t\tLabelSandboxName:  sandboxName,\n475: \t})\n476: \n477: \tidleTimeout := DefaultSandboxIdleTimeout\n478: \tif template.Spec.SessionTimeout != nil {\n479: \t\tidleTimeout = int(template.Spec.SessionTimeout.Duration.Minutes())\n480: \t}\n481: \tcr.SetAnnotations(map[string]string{\n482: \t\tAnnotationIdleTimeout: fmt.Sprintf(\"%dm\", idleTimeout),\n483: \t})\n484: \n485: \tttl := DefaultSandboxTTL\n486: \tif template.Spec.MaxSessionDuration != nil {\n487: \t\tttl = template.Spec.MaxSessionDuration.Duration.Hours()\n488: \t}\n489: \tshutdownTime := time.Now().Add(time.Duration(ttl) * time.Hour)\n490: \n491: \tspec := map[string]interface{}{\n492: \t\t\"replicas\": int64(1),\n493: \t\t\"lifecycle\": map[string]interface{}{\n494: \t\t\t\"shutdownTime\": shutdownTime.Format(time.RFC3339),\n495: \t\t},\n496: \t}\n497: \n498: \tvar portsList []interface{}\n499: \tfor _, p := range ports {\n500: \t\tportsList = append(portsList, map[string]interface{}{\n501: \t\t\t\"name\":     p.Name,\n502: \t\t\t\"port\":     int64(p.Port),\n503: \t\t\t\"protocol\": string(p.Protocol),\n504: \t\t})\n505: \t}\n506: \tif len(portsList) > 0 {\n507: \t\tspec[\"ports\"] = portsList\n508: \t}\n509: \n510: \ttmpl := template.Spec.Template\n511: \tcontainer := corev1.Container{\n512: \t\tName:  \"code-interpreter\",\n513: \t\tImage: tmpl.Image,\n514: \t}\n515: \tif tmpl.ImagePullPolicy != \"\" {\n516: \t\tcontainer.ImagePullPolicy = tmpl.ImagePullPolicy\n517: \t}\n518: \tif len(tmpl.Environment) > 0 {\n519: \t\tcontainer.Env = tmpl.Environment\n520: \t}\n521: \tif len(tmpl.Command) > 0 {\n522: \t\tcontainer.Command = tmpl.Command\n523: \t}\n524: \tif len(tmpl.Args) > 0 {\n525: \t\tcontainer.Args = tmpl.Args\n526: \t}\n527: \tif !reflect.DeepEqual(tmpl.Resources, corev1.ResourceRequirements{}) {\n528: \t\tcontainer.Resources = tmpl.Resources\n529: \t}\n530: \n531: \tpodSpec := corev1.PodSpec{\n532: \t\tContainers: []corev1.Container{container},\n533: \t}\n534: \tif tmpl.RuntimeClassName != nil {\n535: \t\tpodSpec.RuntimeClassName = tmpl.RuntimeClassName\n536: \t}\n537: \tif len(tmpl.ImagePullSecrets) > 0 {\n538: \t\tpodSpec.ImagePullSecrets = tmpl.ImagePullSecrets\n539: \t}\n540: \n541: \tpodSpecMap, err := runtime.DefaultUnstructuredConverter.ToUnstructured(&podSpec)\n542: \tif err != nil {\n543: \t\treturn nil, \"\", fmt.Errorf(\"failed to convert pod spec: %w\", err)\n544: \t}\n545: \tspec[\"podTemplate\"] = podSpecMap\n546: \n547: \tcr.Object[\"spec\"] = spec\n548: \n549: \treturn cr, SandboxesKind, nil\n550: }\n551: \n552: func getPortsOrDefaults(ports []runtimev1alpha1.TargetPort) []runtimev1alpha1.TargetPort {\n553: \tif len(ports) == 0 {\n554: \t\treturn []runtimev1alpha1.TargetPort{\n555: \t\t\t{Port: 8080, Protocol: runtimev1alpha1.ProtocolTypeHTTP, PathPrefix: \"/\"},\n556: \t\t}\n557: \t}\n558: \treturn ports\n559: }\n560: \n561: func (h *SandboxCreateHandler) injectPicodAuthEnv(cr *unstructured.Unstructured, namespace string, clientset kubernetes.Interface) error {\n562: \tsecret, err := clientset.CoreV1().Secrets(namespace).Get(context.Background(), IdentitySecretName, metav1.GetOptions{})\n563: \tif err != nil {\n564: \t\tif apierrors.IsNotFound(err) {\n565: \t\t\treturn fmt.Errorf(\"public key not yet loaded from Router Secret\")\n566: \t\t}\n567: \t\treturn fmt.Errorf(\"failed to get secret: %w\", err)\n568: \t}\n569: \n570: \tpublicKey, ok := secret.Data[PublicKeyDataKey]\n571: \tif !ok || len(publicKey) == 0 {\n572: \t\treturn fmt.Errorf(\"public key not yet loaded from Router Secret\")\n573: \t}\n574: \n575: \tspec, ok := cr.Object[\"spec\"].(map[string]interface{})\n576: \tif !ok {\n577: \t\treturn fmt.Errorf(\"spec not found in CR\")\n578: \t}\n579: \n580: \tpodTemplate, ok := spec[\"podTemplate\"].(map[string]interface{})\n581: \tif !ok {\n582: \t\treturn fmt.Errorf(\"podTemplate not found in spec\")\n583: \t}\n584: \n585: \tcontainers, ok := podTemplate[\"containers\"].([]interface{})\n586: \tif !ok || len(containers) == 0 {\n587: \t\treturn fmt.Errorf(\"containers not found in podTemplate\")\n588: \t}\n589: \n590: \tfirstContainer, ok := containers[0].(map[string]interface{})\n591: \tif !ok {\n592: \t\treturn fmt.Errorf(\"invalid container format\")\n593: \t}\n594: \n595: \tenvVars, ok := firstContainer[\"env\"].([]interface{})\n596: \tif !ok {\n597: \t\tenvVars = []interface{}{}\n598: \t}\n599: \n600: \tnewEnv := map[string]interface{}{\n601: \t\t\"name\":  \"PICOD_AUTH_PUBLIC_KEY\",\n602: \t\t\"value\": string(publicKey),\n603: \t}\n604: \n605: \tfirstContainer[\"env\"] = append(envVars, newEnv)\n606: \tcontainers[0] = firstContainer\n607: \tpodTemplate[\"containers\"] = containers\n608: \tspec[\"podTemplate\"] = podTemplate\n609: \tcr.Object[\"spec\"] = spec\n610: \n611: \treturn nil\n612: }\n613: \n614: func (h *SandboxCreateHandler) resolvePodIP(ctx context.Context, sandboxName, namespace string, sandboxCR *unstructured.Unstructured, clientset kubernetes.Interface) (string, error) {\n615: \tpodLister := h.informerFactory.Core().V1().Pods().Lister()\n616: \n617: \tpod, err := podLister.Pods(namespace).Get(sandboxName)\n618: \tif err == nil && pod.Status.Phase == corev1.PodRunning && pod.Status.PodIP != \"\" {\n619: \t\treturn pod.Status.PodIP, nil\n620: \t}\n621: \n622: \tannotations := sandboxCR.GetAnnotations()\n623: \tif podName, ok := annotations[AnnotationSandboxPodName]; ok && podName != \"\" {\n624: \t\tpod, err := podLister.Pods(namespace).Get(podName)\n625: \t\tif err == nil {\n626: \t\t\tif pod.Status.Phase != corev1.PodRunning {\n627: \t\t\t\treturn \"\", fmt.Errorf(\"pod is not running\")\n628: \t\t\t}\n629: \t\t\tif pod.Status.PodIP == \"\" {\n630: \t\t\t\treturn \"\", fmt.Errorf(\"pod has no IP\")\n631: \t\t\t}\n632: \t\t\treturn pod.Status.PodIP, nil\n633: \t\t}\n634: \t}\n635: \n636: \tpods, err := podLister.Pods(namespace).List(labels.SelectorFromSet(labels.Set{\n637: \t\tLabelSandboxName: sandboxName,\n638: \t}))\n639: \tif err != nil {\n640: \t\treturn \"\", fmt.Errorf(\"pod not found for sandbox\")\n641: \t}\n642: \n643: \tfor _, p := range pods {\n644: \t\tfor _, ownerRef := range p.OwnerReferences {\n645: \t\t\tif ownerRef.Kind == \"Sandbox\" && ownerRef.Name == sandboxName {\n646: \t\t\t\tif p.Status.Phase != corev1.PodRunning {\n647: \t\t\t\t\treturn \"\", fmt.Errorf(\"pod is not running\")\n648: \t\t\t\t}\n649: \t\t\t\tif p.Status.PodIP == \"\" {\n650: \t\t\t\t\treturn \"\", fmt.Errorf(\"pod has no IP\")\n651: \t\t\t\t}\n652: \t\t\t\treturn p.Status.PodIP, nil\n653: \t\t\t}\n654: \t\t}\n655: \t}\n656: \n657: \treturn \"\", fmt.Errorf(\"pod not found for sandbox\")\n658: }\n659: \n660: func (h *SandboxCreateHandler) buildEntryPoints(podIP string, ports []runtimev1alpha1.TargetPort) []EntryPoint {\n661: \tvar entryPoints []EntryPoint\n662: \tfor _, p := range ports {\n663: \t\tentryPoints = append(entryPoints, EntryPoint{\n664: \t\t\tPath:     p.PathPrefix,\n665: \t\t\tProtocol: string(p.Protocol),\n666: \t\t\tEndpoint: fmt.Sprintf(\"%s:%d\", podIP, p.Port),\n667: \t\t})\n668: \t}\n669: \treturn entryPoints\n670: }\n671: \n672: func generateSessionID() string {\n673: \treturn uuid.New().String()\n674: }\n675: \n676: func generateSandboxName(workloadName string) string {\n677: \treturn fmt.Sprintf(\"%s-%s\", workloadName, RandString(8))\n678: }\n679: \n680: func RandString(n int) string {\n681: \tconst charset = \"abcdefghijklmnopqrstuvwxyzABCDEFGHIJKLMNOPQRSTUVWXYZ0123456789\"\n682: \tb := make([]byte, n)\n683: \tfor i := range b {\n684: \t\tb[i] = charset[rand.Intn(len(charset))]\n685: \t}\n686: \treturn string(b)\n687: }\n\n(End of file - total 687 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"package handler\n\nimport (\n\t\"context\"\n\t\"fmt\"\n\t\"log\"\n\t\"math/rand\"\n\t\"net/http\"\n\t\"time\"\n\n\t\"github.com/gin-gonic/gin\"\n\t\"github.com/google/uuid\"\n\tcorev1 \"k8s.io/api/core/v1\"\n\tapierrors \"k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/api/errors\"\n\tmetav1 \"k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/apis/meta/v1\"\n\t\"k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/apis/meta/v1/unstructured\"\n\t\"k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/labels\"\n\t\"k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/runtime\"\n\t\"k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/runtime/schema\"\n\t\"k8s.io/client-go/dynamic\"","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/pkg/workloadmanager/handler/sandbox_create.go","time":{"start":1775818505902,"end":1775818505909}}}}
