{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775818513551,"sessionID":"ses_288fc3978ffestAwKqA90pStH5","part":{"id":"prt_d7708182c001oCmnc0A3V1iggu","messageID":"msg_d7707fef4001zH7qKHX2owV2jV","sessionID":"ses_288fc3978ffestAwKqA90pStH5","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"call_77808ba341134473b408eab2","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/session-store/design.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/session-store/design.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # Session Store — Design\n2: \n3: ## Module\n4: \n5: - `github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube` — versions in sandbox-orchestration `design.md`.\n6: \n7: ## Package `github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/pkg/store`\n8: \n9: ### Store interface (exact signatures)\n10: \n11: ```go\n12: package store\n13: \n14: import (\n15:     \"context\"\n16:     \"time\"\n17: \n18:     \"github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/pkg/common/types\"\n19: )\n20: \n21: type Store interface {\n22:     Ping(ctx context.Context) error\n23:     GetSandboxBySessionID(ctx context.Context, sessionID string) (*types.SandboxInfo, error)\n24:     StoreSandbox(ctx context.Context, sandboxStore *types.SandboxInfo) error\n25:     UpdateSandbox(ctx context.Context, sandboxStore *types.SandboxInfo) error\n26:     DeleteSandboxBySessionID(ctx context.Context, sessionID string) error\n27:     ListExpiredSandboxes(ctx context.Context, before time.Time, limit int64) ([]*types.SandboxInfo, error)\n28:     ListInactiveSandboxes(ctx context.Context, before time.Time, limit int64) ([]*types.SandboxInfo, error)\n29:     UpdateSessionLastActivity(ctx context.Context, sessionID string, at time.Time) error\n30:     Close() error\n31: }\n32: ```\n33: \n34: ### Errors\n35: \n36: ```go\n37: var ErrNotFound = errors.New(\"store: not found\")\n38: ```\n39: \n40: ### Provider type constants (`singleton.go`)\n41: \n42: ```go\n43: const (\n44:     redisStoreType  string = \"redis\"\n45:     valkeyStoreType string = \"valkey\"\n46: )\n47: ```\n48: \n49: ### Singleton\n50: \n51: ```go\n52: var (\n53:     initStoreOnce = &sync.Once{}\n54:     provider      Store\n55: )\n56: \n57: func Storage() Store\n58: func initStore() error\n59: ```\n60: \n61: - `Storage()` calls `initStoreOnce.Do(initStore)`; on error `klog.Fatalf(\"init store failed: %v\", err)`.\n62: \n63: ### Sandbox document type\n64: \n65: Stored JSON unmarshals to `github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/pkg/common/types.SandboxInfo`:\n66: \n67: ```go\n68: type SandboxInfo struct {\n69:     Kind             string              `json:\"kind\"`\n70:     SandboxID        string              `json:\"sandboxId\"`\n71:     SandboxNamespace string              `json:\"sandboxNamespace\"`\n72:     Name             string              `json:\"name\"`\n73:     EntryPoints      []SandboxEntryPoint `json:\"entryPoints\"`\n74:     SessionID        string              `json:\"sessionId\"`\n75:     CreatedAt        time.Time           `json:\"createdAt\"`\n76:     ExpiresAt        time.Time           `json:\"expiresAt\"`\n77:     Status           string              `json:\"status\"`\n78: }\n79: \n80: type SandboxEntryPoint struct {\n81:     Path     string `json:\"path\"`\n82:     Protocol string `json:\"protocol\"`\n83:     Endpoint string `json:\"endpoint\"`\n84: }\n85: ```\n86: \n87: ## Redis implementation (`store_redis.go`)\n88: \n89: ### Struct\n90: \n91: ```go\n92: type redisStore struct {\n93:     cli                  *redisv9.Client  // github.com/redis/go-redis/v9\n94:     sessionPrefix        string\n95:     expiryIndexKey       string\n96:     lastActivityIndexKey string\n97: }\n98: ```\n99: \n100: ### Fixed key patterns\n101: \n102: | Field | Value |\n103: |-------|--------|\n104: | `sessionPrefix` | `\"session:\"` |\n105: | `expiryIndexKey` | `\"session:expiry\"` |\n106: | `lastActivityIndexKey` | `\"session:last_activity\"` |\n107: \n108: ### Connection options (`makeRedisOptions`)\n109: \n110: ```go\n111: return &redisv9.Options{\n112:     Addr:     redisAddr,     // REDIS_ADDR\n113:     Password: redisPassword, // REDIS_PASSWORD\n114: }, nil\n115: ```\n116: \n117: ### Environment variables (Redis)\n118: \n119: | Variable | Required | Notes |\n120: |----------|----------|--------|\n121: | `REDIS_ADDR` | Yes | |\n122: | `REDIS_PASSWORD` | Yes unless `REDIS_PASSWORD_REQUIRED=false` | Case-insensitive compare to `\"false\"` |\n123: | `STORE_TYPE` | No | Default `redis` |\n124: \n125: ### Operations summary\n126: \n127: | Method | Redis commands |\n128: |--------|----------------|\n129: | `Ping` | `PING` → expect `PONG` |\n130: | `GetSandboxBySessionID` | `GET session:{id}` |\n131: | `StoreSandbox` | Pipeline: `SETNX`, `ZADD session:expiry`, `ZADD session:last_activity` |\n132: | `UpdateSandbox` | `SET key value XX` |\n133: | `DeleteSandboxBySessionID` | Pipeline: `DEL`, `ZREM expiry`, `ZREM last_activity` |\n134: | `ListExpiredSandboxes` | `ZRANGEBYSCORE session:expiry -inf {before.Unix} LIMIT 0 limit` then pipeline GETs |\n135: | `ListInactiveSandboxes` | `ZRANGEBYSCORE session:last_activity ...` then pipeline GETs |\n136: | `UpdateSessionLastActivity` | `GET` (existence), then `ZADD session:last_activity` |\n137: | `Close` | `cli.Close()` |\n138: \n139: - `List*` with `limit <= 0` returns `nil, nil`.\n140: - `sessionKey(id)` → `sessionPrefix + sessionID`.\n141: \n142: ## Valkey implementation (`store_valkey.go`)\n143: \n144: ### Struct\n145: \n146: ```go\n147: type valkeyStore struct {\n148:     cli                  valkey.Client  // github.com/valkey-io/valkey-go\n149:     sessionPrefix        string\n150:     expiryIndexKey       string\n151:     lastActivityIndexKey string\n152: }\n153: ```\n154: \n155: Same string constants as Redis for prefix and ZSET keys.\n156: \n157: ### Connection options (`makeValkeyOptions`)\n158: \n159: ```go\n160: valkeyClientOptions := &valkey.ClientOption{\n161:     InitAddress: strings.Split(valkeyAddr, \",\"),\n162:     Password:    valkeyPassword,\n163: }\n164: ```\n165: \n166: Optional: `DisableCache` from `VALKEY_DISABLE_CACHE` (ParseBool, must be true); `ForceSingleClient` from `VALKEY_FORCE_SINGLE` (ParseBool, must be true).\n167: \n168: ### Environment variables (Valkey)\n169: \n170: | Variable | Required | Notes |\n171: |----------|----------|--------|\n172: | `VALKEY_ADDR` | Yes | Comma-separated list → `InitAddress` |\n173: | `VALKEY_PASSWORD` | Yes unless `VALKEY_PASSWORD_REQUIRED=false` | |\n174: | `VALKEY_DISABLE_CACHE` | No | `\"true\"` enables `DisableCache` |\n175: | `VALKEY_FORCE_SINGLE` | No | `\"true\"` enables `ForceSingleClient` |\n176: | `STORE_TYPE` | Must be `valkey` | Case-insensitive |\n177: \n178: ### Operations summary\n179: \n180: | Method | Valkey API |\n181: |--------|------------|\n182: | `Ping` | `B().Ping()` → string `PONG` |\n183: | `GetSandboxBySessionID` | `B().Get().Key(key)` → bytes; `IsValkeyNil` → `ErrNotFound` |\n184: | `StoreSandbox` | `DoMulti`: `SETNX`, `ZADD` expiry, `ZADD` last_activity |\n185: | `UpdateSandbox` | `SET ... XX`; success requires `ToString() == \"OK\"` |\n186: | `DeleteSandboxBySessionID` | `DoMulti`: `DEL`, `ZREM` expiry, `ZREM` last_activity |\n187: | `ListExpiredSandboxes` | `Zrangebyscore` with `Min(\"-inf\")`, `Max(fmt.Sprintf(\"%d\", before.Unix()))`, `Limit(0, limit)` |\n188: | `ListInactiveSandboxes` | Same on `last_activity` key |\n189: | `UpdateSessionLastActivity` | `Exists` key → int64 must be 1; then `Zadd` |\n190: | `Close` | `vs.cli.Close()` then return nil |\n191: \n192: ### ZSET score semantics\n193: \n194: - **Expiry index:** score = `float64(sandboxRedis.ExpiresAt.Unix())` on store.\n195: - **Last activity:** score = `float64(time.Now().Unix())` on `StoreSandbox`; `float64(at.Unix())` on `UpdateSessionLastActivity`.\n196: \n197: ### MGET note (Valkey)\n198: \n199: - `loadSandboxesBySessionIDs` builds all `session:{id}` keys and uses single `Mget`; comment states keys should be in same slot (deployment consideration).\n200: \n201: ## Dependencies (store package imports)\n202: \n203: - `github.com/redis/go-redis/v9`\n204: - `github.com/valkey-io/valkey-go`\n205: - `k8s.io/klog/v2` (Valkey options logging)\n206: - `github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/pkg/common/types`\n\n(End of file - total 206 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# Session Store — Design\n\n## Module\n\n- `github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube` — versions in sandbox-orchestration `design.md`.\n\n## Package `github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/pkg/store`\n\n### Store interface (exact signatures)\n\n```go\npackage store\n\nimport (\n    \"context\"\n    \"time\"\n\n    \"github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/pkg/common/types\"\n)\n","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/session-store/design.md","time":{"start":1775818513541,"end":1775818513549}}}}
